{"tid":1864910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［仆街大伏］信報：政府只能收幾千人檢疫，其他人只能‘居家隔離’，再派人抽樣檢查！","createTime":"2020-02-06T01:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T02:42:29.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a5856d80d17132c22b971c098299aa3fa102f2","tid":1864910,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯有政府中人估計，官方最多只能承受數千人留港強制檢疫，若高於此數，執行上極為困難；換言之，新措施能否奏效，關鍵是從內地入境人數會否日內進一步大幅縮減。<br />\n<br />\n翻查政府周一公布再封4個主要口岸後，翌日依然有超過兩萬人從深圳灣入境（包括香港居民和內地旅客），由內地經空路來港的也有6000人。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯粗略估算即使當中有五成人嫌麻煩卻步，每天循內地過關的人數仍有逾萬人。一萬人在香港境內進行「家居隔離」究竟是有助控制疫情，還是增加了社區播毒風險，實屬疑問。<br />\n<br />\n（信報計錯數，係一萬人*14=14萬人'家居隔離&lsquo;）<br />\n<br />\n措施另一漏洞是只強制從「內地」來港人士檢疫14天，那麼由澳門經港珠澳大橋入境者，是否該納入「內地」範圍需接受隔離？若然不是，假如澳門疫情一發不可收拾，港府將中門大開，任由濠江帶菌者直闖境內，屆時再封大橋口岸恐怕已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n另一棘手問題是執行細節。由於隔離營短缺，可以預期政府所謂的強制檢疫，有關人士不會全數入住隔離營，應屬「家居隔離」為主。據了解，當局僅靠跨部門成立的突擊檢查隊，上門抽查隔離人士有否違規。可是如果有人在期間逃脫，又可怎樣應對？消息人士透露，政府將派人票控，最嚴重可判監半年。不過，官方就怎樣追蹤逃脫人士，暫無清晰說法。<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2371422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2371422&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=6ea63533\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2371422</a><br />\n<br />\n之後病撚咗咪又係香港醫<br />\n屌你老母咁有乜用"},{"pid":"96fdc43b82333105ec99fab0355d926b6160301f","tid":1864910,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97296953ab58a604ba41728d988c3b60c0b161cb","tid":1864910,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"根本無地方隔離，陣間d人又周圍走<br />\n應該要全面關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6505d6ad77c9d21c589b217fb7b8e309c64a1e","tid":1864910,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"即係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ed76aabe89e67435a117862c738e5d43d26edb","tid":1864910,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"檢疫 = 自律留屋企量體溫"},{"pid":"5a8fc1ea0baf6c1849a54fca9dd7234ec5c98270","tid":1864910,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"佢前幾日咪打撚曬飛機話有新科技冇gps嘅電子手環呀嘛<br />\n你地要相信政府唔驚先得㗎"},{"pid":"26b2a082802ee67eab4a98a6f5fa1b75229d8ca4","tid":1864910,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2bhVfn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2bhVfn.png&h=2dc72513&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ca7802eba15d13e32b3a85273148d3a449842e9","tid":1864910,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24d3918658364b4a0c381a0f251d48db991818c9","tid":1864910,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"等運到 生物演化証實 運氣比一切都重要"},{"pid":"6025e70524798052e78535faf1038defd9e1427b","tid":1864910,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"政府根本就係想攬炒<br />\n費事美孚又嘈，西貢又嘈<br />\n大家返屋企自我隔離，咁就唔洗出來反對<br />\n全城都係隔離中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b973932c847a3c09e55e988d1a337e99c25837d4","tid":1864910,"uid":127624,"l